    "description": "## ITCure API Tests\n\nThis collection contains automated tests for the ITCure API. The tests are organized by feature and cover the main API endpoints.\n\n### Test credentials\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Email | `test@test.com` |\n| Password | `Test!12345` |",
